        alt="what is the face haus">
      <div class="about_head_2">HAUS + HOME</div>
      <p>Skin care isn’t the only kind of caring we do around here. As a growing brand, we realize we have an
        opportunity to make a difference in our communities. We have a Haus to call our own, but not everyone is as
        fortunate—so we’ve made a commitment to help in the fight against homelessness.</p>
      <p>This year, Face Haus is continuing its mission by partnering with BOMBAS, the one-for-one sock brand that
        donates a pair of socks for each pair sold. Bombas and Face Haus have introduced a signature FH mint green
        sock design – currently sold at all Face Haus locations. With each sock purchase, a pair will be donated to
        organizations combating homelessness in all of our Haus communities: Midnight Mission (Los Angeles), The
        Bridge Homeless Recovery Center (Dallas), and the Bowery Mission Women’s Residence (New York). </p>
      <p>Our local Face Haus teams have also had the enriching opportunity to work across these three organizations as
        volunteers for community meals and giving events. </p>
      <p>Stay tuned for updates and opportunities on our website and social feeds as we do our part to brighten the
        lives of those in need.</p>
